    <abstract id="aspace_379bf472d14325cc23b08add421d4edd">The records of Voegtly Evangelical Church contain church history, registers, bulletins, and cemetery records, 1833-1981.</abstract>
    <langmaterial>
      <language langcode="eng">English</language>
.    </langmaterial>
